==Mandarin==
===Etymology===
From: [[第一]] the first + [[把]] [[measure word]] + [[交椅]] chair with a high back and arms
===Idiom===
{{cmn-idiom|ts|pin=dìyī bă jiāoyĭ|pint=di4yi1ba3jiao1yi3|rs=竹05}}
